# SASS Installation Steps


1. Installed Node Version Manager (NVM) to manage Node.js versions:
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash


2. Closed and reopened the terminal to activate NVM.


3. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using NVM (if not already installed):
   $ nvm install 20.16
   $ nvm use 20.16


4. Verified Node.js and npm installation:
   $ node -v
   $ npm -v


5. Installed SASS compiler version 3.7.4 globally using npm:
   $ npm install sass@3.7.4


6. Verified SASS installation:
   $ sass --version
